  "cooking_instructions": [
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Boil a kettle</p>\n<p>Heat a dry pot over a medium heat</p>\n<p>Once hot, add the <strong>pine nuts </strong>and cook for 2-3 min or until golden and toasted</p>\n<p>Tip: watch the nuts like a hawk to make sure they don't burn!</p>\n<p>Once done, transfer them to a plate and set aside, reserving the pot</p>",
      "order": 1,
      "image": "/images/instructions/purple-sprouting-broccoli-lemon-linguine/step-1.jpg"
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>linguine</strong> to the reserved pot with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong></p>\n<p>Cover with plenty of <strong>boiled water</strong> and bring to the boil over a high heat</p>\n<p>Cook the<strong> linguine</strong> for an initial 4-5 min</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "image": "/images/instructions/purple-sprouting-broccoli-lemon-linguine/step-2.jpg"
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, re-boil a kettle</p>\n<p>Cut the <strong>purple sprouting broccoli</strong> in half </p>\n<p>Dissolve the <strong>vegetable stock cube<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong> in 150ml <span class=\"text-danger\">[300ml]</span> <strong>boiled water</strong></p>",
      "order": 3,
      "image": "/images/instructions/purple-sprouting-broccoli-lemon-linguine/step-3.jpg"
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the <strong>linguine</strong> has had 4-5 min, add the<strong> chopped broccoli</strong></p>\n<p>Cook for a further 4-5 min until everything's tender</p>\n<p>Once tender, drain and keep in the sieve</p>\n<p>Reserve the pot for later</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "image": "/images/instructions/purple-sprouting-broccoli-lemon-linguine/step-4.jpg"
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, peel and finely slice (don't chop!) the <strong>garlic </strong></p>\n<p>Zest 1/2 <span class=\"text-danger\">[1] </span><strong>lemon </strong>and cut the<strong> lemon<span class=\"text-danger\">[s] </span></strong>in half</p>\n<p> </p>",
      "order": 5,
      "image": "/images/instructions/purple-sprouting-broccoli-lemon-linguine/step-5.jpg"
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Return the reserved pot to a medium heat with 2 tbsp <span class=\"text-danger\">[4 tbsp]</span> <strong>olive oil</strong></p>\n<p>Once hot, add the<strong> sliced</strong> <strong>garlic </strong>and cook for 2-3 min or until starting to soften </p>",
      "order": 6,
      "image": "/images/instructions/purple-sprouting-broccoli-lemon-linguine/step-6.jpg"
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Return the <strong>drained linguine</strong><strong> </strong>and<strong> broccoli</strong> to the pot with the <strong>vegetable stock </strong>and <strong>lemon zest</strong> </p>\n<p>Squeeze in the<strong> juice</strong> of 1/2 <span class=\"text-danger\">[1]</span> <strong>lemon</strong> and add the <strong>grated Italian hard cheese</strong> </p>\n<p>Give everything a good mix up – this is your<strong> Purple Sprouting Broccoli &amp; Lemon Linguine </strong></p>\n<p>Tip: add a drizzle more olive oil if your pasta is looking a little dry</p>",
      "order": 7,
      "image": "/images/instructions/purple-sprouting-broccoli-lemon-linguine/step-7.jpg"
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Cut the <strong>remaining</strong> <strong>lemon</strong> into wedges</p>\n<p>Serve the <strong>Purple Sprouting Broccoli &amp; Lemon Linguine</strong> topped with the <strong>rocket</strong></p>\n<p>Sprinkle with the<strong> toasted pine nuts</strong>,<strong> </strong>then season with a good grind of <strong>black pepper</strong> and a drizzle of <strong>olive oil </strong></p>\n<p>Garnish with a wedge of<strong> lemon </strong>and enjoy!</p>",
      "order": 8
    }
